            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1960-03-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-02-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="[Unnumbered document following Document 710 (#41)]" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d710a-41">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>—At the morning meeting of the Foreign Ministers (<hi rend="italic">ante</hi>,
                    page 145) it was agreed that they would meet at 3:45 p.m. The <hi rend="italic">Rapporteur’s</hi> report (<hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, page 158) indicates
                    that the meeting was actually held, but no minutes therefor have been found.</p>
            </div>
